      505.48,
      533.97,
      565.51
    ],
    "text": "According to the today\u2019s (May 15th) latest weather analysis, the low-pressure area located northeast of the Sri Lanka, still persist. The Department of Meteorology is continuously monitoring the behavior, development and path of the system.",
