      392.93,
      98.74,
      404.93
    ],
    "text": "Winds:",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      61.34,
      414.65,
      557.34,
      460.37
    ],
    "text": "Winds will be South-westerly. Wind speed will be (25-35) kmph. Wind speed can increase up to (50-60) kmph at times in the sea areas off the coast extending from Trincomalee to Pottuvil via Kankasanthurai, Puttalam, Colombo, Galle and Hambantota.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      61.34,
      470.23,
      126.69,
      482.23
    ],
    "text": "State of Sea:",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      61.34,
      492.07,
      557.63,
      604.15
    ],
    "text": "The sea areas off the coasts extending from Trincomalee to Pottuvil via Kankasanthurai, Puttalam, Colombo, Galle and Hambantota will be rough at times. The other sea areas around the island can be moderate. The swell waves (about 2.0 \u2013 2.5 m) height (this is not for land area) may increase in the sea areas off the coast extending from Puttalam to Pottuvil via Colombo, Galle and Hambantota. Temporarily strong gusty winds and very rough seas can be expected during thundershowers.",
